Thunderbirds Are Go is a CGI TV series made by ITV Studios and Pukeko Pictures, with effects by Weta Workshop.

It is a remake of the original Thunderbirds series.

It premiered on 4 April 2015. The majority of the main characters from the 1960s series have returned, including the five Tracy brothers (Scott, John, Virgil, Gordon, and Alan), Brains, Lady Penelope and Parker, Grandma Tracy, The Hood and Tintin (Renamed Kayo)
